--INSERT INTO TMP_FCT_AR_SMY_PRJ_FPF (ar_id, cl_ar_smy_tp_id, cl_smy_adl_tp_id, eff_dt, end_dt, cl_id, char_value, number_value, date_value, tech_crc)
  SELECT ar_id,
         cl_ar_smy_tp_id,
         cl_smy_adl_tp_id,
         eff_dt,
         end_dt,
         cl_id,
         char_value,
         number_value,
         date_value,
         md5 (cl_id || '#' || char_value || '#' || number_value || '#' || date_value/*, 'SHA1'*/) AS tech_crc
  FROM
    (SELECT cast(md5('CGD#GD#'||'VEB_CRM_INVEST_PRCT#'|| TO_CHAR (gg.id, 'FM9999')/*, 'SHA1'*/) as varchar(40)) as  ar_id,
            cl.cl_ar_smy_tp_id,
            '107B2B5E1DC55F3F9577EAFB7C90EF266CA5E4B9' AS cl_smy_adl_tp_id, -- Не определено
			date_trunc('year',gg.valid_from) AS eff_dt,
			--decode(date_trunc('year',gg.valid_to), date '2299-12-31', date '3000-01-01', date_trunc('year',gg.valid_to)) AS end_dt,
			case 
				when date_trunc('year',gg.valid_to) = date '2299-12-31' then date '3000-01-01'
				else date_trunc('year',gg.valid_to)
			end as end_dt,
			NULL AS cl_id,
			cast(NULL AS varchar(1024)) AS char_value,
			gg.prj_ofzin AS number_value,
			NULL AS date_value
     FROM dwh_dv.cgd_gd_veb_crm_invest_prct_day_diff gg
     INNER JOIN dwh_bv.vcl_ar_smy_tp cl ON cl.cl_ar_smy_tp_bk = 'PRJ_OFZIN'
     INNER JOIN dwh_bv.dim_ar ar ON ar.ar_id = md5('CGD#GD#'||'VEB_CRM_INVEST_PRCT#'|| to_char(gg.id, 'FM9999')/*, 'SHA1'*/) -- 
     WHERE 1=1
       AND gg.status = 1
	   AND coalesce(gg.arh_project, 0) = 0 --NVL(gg.arh_project, 0) = 0
       AND gg.prj_ofzin <> 0
       and gg.valid_from < v_end_dt /*date'2023-09-28'*/
       and gg.valid_to  >= v_start_dt +1  /*date'2023-10-01' + 1*/
       and date_trunc('year',gg.valid_from) <> date_trunc('year',gg.valid_to))t
